Package hu.sztaki.sztakipediaparser.wiki.tags

Provides the node classes of the abstract syntax tree.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AbstractTag An abstract class, it is the parent class of all classes that represent a node in the abstract syntax tree.
AnchorTag Represents an anchor in the AST.
BodyTag Represents the root node of the AST.
BoldTag Represents a bold tag in the AST.
DivTag Represents a div tag in the AST.
HeadingTag Represents a section heading in the AST.
HRTag Represents a horizontal ruler in the AST.
ImageTag Represents an image in the AST.
IndentTag Represents indentation in the AST.
ItalicTag Represents an italic tag in the AST.
ParagraphTag Represents a paragraph tag in the AST.
RawWikiTag Represents raw wiki content in the AST.
ReferenceTag Represents a citation in the AST.
StringTag Represents any free text in the AST.
TableCaptionTag Represents a table's caption in the AST.
TableCellTag Represents a table cell in the AST.
TableColHeadingTag Represents a table column heading in the AST.
TableRowHeadingTag Represents a table row heading in the AST.
TableRowTag Represents a table row in the AST.
TableTag Represents a table in the AST.
TemplateParam A class for storing template parameters.
TemplateTag Represents a wiki template in the AST.
UnorderedListItemTag Represents an item of an unordered list in the AST.
UnorderedListTag Represents an unordered list in the AST.
